changelog/README.rst
     1‚ÜíThis directory contains "newsfragments" which are short files that contain a small **ReST**-formatted
     2‚Üítext that will be added to the next ``CHANGELOG``.
     3‚Üí
     4‚ÜíThe ``CHANGELOG`` will be read by users, so this description should be aimed to pytest users
     5‚Üíinstead of describing internal changes which are only relevant to the developers.
     6‚Üí
     7‚ÜíMake sure to use full sentences with correct case and punctuation, for example::
     8‚Üí
     9‚Üí    Fix issue with non-ascii messages from the ``warnings`` module.
    10‚Üí
