    40‚Üíclass HookspecOpts(TypedDict):
    42‚Üí
    43‚Üí    #: Whether the hook is :ref:`first result only <firstresult>`.
    44‚Üí    firstresult: bool
    45‚Üí    #: Whether the hook is :ref:`historic <historic>`.
    46‚Üí    historic: bool
    47‚Üí    #: Whether the hook :ref:`warns when implemented <warn_on_impl>`.
    48‚Üí    warn_on_impl: Warning | None
    49‚Üí    #: Whether the hook warns when :ref:`certain arguments are requested
    50‚Üí    #: <warn_on_impl>`.
    51‚Üí    #:
    52‚Üí    #: .. versionadded:: 1.5
