    61‚Üí    #: Whether the hook implementation is an :ref:`old-style wrapper
    62‚Üí    #: <old_style_hookwrappers>`.
    63‚Üí    hookwrapper: bool
    64‚Üí    #: Whether validation against a hook specification is :ref:`optional
